kground-color: #f2f0f5;\">[Example.com]# make install</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 16px;\">Start the Apache:-</span></strong></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; background-color: #f2f0f5; color: #333399;\">[Example.com]# /etc/init.d/httpd start</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">or</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; background-color: #f2f0f5; color: #333399;\">[Example.com]#apachetl -k start</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 16px;\">To Stop :-</span></strong></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #333399; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #333399; background-color: #f2f0f5;\">[Example.com]# /etc/init.d/httpd stop</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">or</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #333399; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #333399; background-color: #f2f0f5;\">[Example.com]#apachetl -k stop</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<wbr />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Times New Roman;\">Permanent Configuration:-</span></strong></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #333399; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #333399; background-color: #f2f0f5;\">[Example.com]# chkconfig httpd on</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">To check whether it is running or not:-</span></strong></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Ti