lor: #f2f0f5;\">[Example.com]# make install</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 16px;\">Start the Apache:-</span></strong></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; background-color: #f2f0f5; color: #333399;\">[Example.com]# /etc/init.d/httpd start</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">or</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; background-color: #f2f0f5; color: #333399;\">[Example.com]#apachetl -k start</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 16px;\">To Stop :-</span></strong></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #333399; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #333399; background-color: #f2f0f5;\">[Example.com]# /etc/init.d/httpd stop</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">or</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #333399; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #333399; background-color: #f2f0f5;\">[Example.com]#apachetl -k stop</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<wbr />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Times New Roman;\">Permanent Configuration:-</span></strong></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #333399; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #333399; background-color: #f2f0f5;\">[Example.com]# chkconfig httpd on</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">To check whether it is running or not:-</span></strong></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #333399; background-color: #ffffff;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #333399; background-color: #f2f0f5;\">[Example.com]# netstat -tulpn | grep :80</span></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<article><strong><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">Further configuration:-</span></strong></article></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">Check the </span><a style=\"color: #0000ff; font-family: Times New Roman;\" href=\"https://httpd.apache.org/\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">Apache website</span></a><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\"> for detailed configuration about the httpd.conf as per your requirements</span></div>', 'How to install Apache HTTPD', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '47-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-10 09:27:38', '2016-01-10 03:57:38', '', '47', 'http://localhost/thatislinux.com/2016/01/10/47-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0' ); ";i:708;s:1231:"INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES( '173', '1', '2016-01-13 03:47:29', '2016-01-12 22:17:29', 'thatisLinux.com helps you in knowing about the Linux basics to advanced topics &amp; also great tutorials.\n\n<strong>\nOverview:-\n</strong>\nWe concentrate on the simple to major installation of software\'s that are used in current software web development projects such as\n<ul>\n	<li> Software development tools for the website</li>\n	<li> Linux administration scripts &amp; Ideas</li>\n	<li> Cloud computing</li>\n	<li> Networking/DNS/Firewalls</li>\n	<li> Best Practices</li>\n</ul>\nSimple tutorials in layman English helps you in understanding well about the topics which is self explanatory with lot of screen shots.\n\nConnect us on<a href=\"https://plus.google.com/u/0/111641777437636327729/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"author\">Google Plus</a>, <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a>, and Youtube. Or send an email us at bala15ozone@gmail.com.\n\n&nbsp;', 'About', '', 'inherit